<section xmlns:ns1="http://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>32-704</num>
  <heading>Domestic partnership benefits.</heading>
  <text>All health care facilities, including hospitals, convalescent facilities, or other long term care facilities, shall allow a patient’s family member as defined in § <cite path="§32-701">32-701</cite>(7) to visit the patient.</text>
